shortDescription:
COVERGIRL Advanced Radiance Age-Defying Liquid Foundation, 150 Creamy Beige, 1 fl oz

The COVERGIRL Advanced Radiance Age Defying Foundation Makeup will help you defy your age with crease-proof, radiant coverage. This liquid foundation leaves behind a breathable, natural matte finish that is never cakey, thanks to its exclusive Olay Amino-Peptide Complex. Whether you're wearing this anti-aging foundation on bare skin for a healthy glow or as the perfect finishing touch over primer and concealer, this can be your go-to solution for fighting wrinkles and dullness without sacrificing radiance.
